    def require_no_conflicted_actor(self, *, actor, approval_case_id) -> None: ...
```

### Implementation Hides

- Borrower as Director.
- Borrower as committee member.
- Relative of Director.
- Material interest.
- Maker-checker conflicts.
- Excluded approvers.

